name: CyberPaw (ISU Game Dev Club)
description:
CyberPaw is a 2D platformer Run-n-Gun. You play as an old fashion western cat lost in a futuristic cyber city. You must use your arsenal of wild west themed weapons to take down the evil cyber animals that stand in your way!

This project was developed by the members of the ISU Game Development Club in the Fall of 2022. For more information on how to get involved with the club, reference the contact information on the following page: https://redbirdlife.illinoisstate.edu/organization/gdc
